<HEADLINE>
AL GORE PREPARES FOR HIS BIG CLOSE-UP 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
 By RICHARD L. BERKE   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
