<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-14 12:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0979 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r l BC-SCOOTER-CRAZE-HNS &LR;      08-14 0460
