Berlin's plans for memorials to Jews. By Roger Cohen.
</P>
<P>
   ANTIQUITIES-COMMISSION (Undated) _ Proposed appointment to
antiquities commission stirs furor. By William H. Honan.
</P>
<P>
   NEW-ORLEANS-ARMSTRONG (New Orleans) _ Retracing Louis
Armstrong's steps in New Orleans. By Ralph Blumenthal.
</P>
<P>
   TIBET-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ Michiko Kakutani reviews ``Virtual
Tibet,'' by Orville Schell.
</P>
<P>
   TV-BULL-REVIEW (Undated) _ On TNT, ``Bull.'' Reviewed by Caryn
James.
