<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-14 15:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1235 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a BC-SCI-BRODY-HEALTH-NYT &LR;      08-14 1119
