<P>
   RUSSIA-SUNK-SUB (Moscow) _ Russian nuclear-powered sub with more
than 100 crew aboard sinks in the Barents sea in more than 300 feet
of water after a collision. Diving bell is in contact, but
prospects look grim. By David Filipov. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; POLITICS (p) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   DEMS-CONVENTION (Los Angeles) _ Democrats get their convention
in gear, with addresses by the Clintons following an opening prayer
by a Roman Catholic cardinal suggesting the unborn be protected. By
Michael Kranish and Ann Scales. 1500 words.
</P>
