It is what unites them even when their specific agendas overlap or
conflict. By Lynda Gorov. 1100 words.
</P>
<P>
   DEMS-INSIDE (Los Angeles) _ Being a Democrat from Texas ain't
worth squat. By Sam Allis. 850 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
