   THOMPSON-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Just what we needed _ another confession/apology from
Bill Clinton. For reasons known only to the self-indulgent,
lame-duck penitent in chief, President Clinton showed up at a
ministers' conference in Illinois and rehashed his oh-so-horrible
feelings of guilt and remorse regarding the White House sex
scandal. By BILL THOMPSON. Story has moved in ``k'' commentary
category. &QL; 
