<SLUG> BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times
News Service Macintosh graphics files that moved Monday, 08/14/00.
Included is the corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics
have been posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo
Database.
